## Performance Checklist

### Load Testing

- [ ] Load test conducted with target concurrent user count
- [ ] Response times measured under load (P50, P95, P99)
- [ ] Targets from nfr-4 are met
- [ ] Database query performance validated
- [ ] API endpoints tested at expected throughput

**Load Test Results:**
- P50 latency: [#]ms (target: [#]ms) ✓/✗
- P95 latency: [#]ms (target: [#]ms) ✓/✗
- P99 latency: [#]ms (target: [#]ms) ✓/✗
- Throughput: [#] req/s (target: [#] req/s) ✓/✗

### Frontend Performance

- [ ] Bundle size measured and within limits (e.g., <500KB)
- [ ] Time to Interactive (TTI) measured and acceptable
- [ ] Lighthouse score ≥80 (performance)
- [ ] Critical rendering path optimized (above-the-fold)
- [ ] Unused dependencies removed

### Backend Performance

- [ ] Slow query logs analyzed and optimized
- [ ] Database indexes created for hot queries
- [ ] Connection pooling configured
- [ ] Caching strategy implemented (Redis/memcached if needed)
- [ ] Bottlenecks identified and addressed

### Monitoring

- [ ] Application performance monitoring (APM) tool integrated
- [ ] Key metrics identified (latency, throughput, error rate)
- [ ] Alerts configured for performance degradation
- [ ] Dashboards set up for ops team

