### Quality Gates

- **90-100:** ✅ GO - Ready for production release
- **80-89:** ⚠️ CONDITIONAL GO - Minor issues, low risk
- **70-79:** 🔴 NO-GO / ITERATE - Address critical gaps before release
- **<70:** 🛑 ESCALATE - Major issues, needs stakeholder decision

